info.author: Rich Harkins
info.description:
Python Dictionary Chaining Module

        Provides a new Python type, dictchain, which can be used to combine
        the contents of multiple other dictionaries into a single dictionary
        front-end.  When requests are made of a dictchain, the chained
        dictionaries are then searched.
info.name: pychains
info.html_description:
Python Dictionary Chaining Module

Provides a new Python type, dictchain, which can be used to combine the contents of multiple other dictionaries into a single dictionary front-end. When requests are made of a dictchain, the chained dictionaries are then searched.
